#. # NOTE: Used for the new http://www.mozilla.org/firefox/new
#: firefox/new.lang:5
msgid "Firefox for desktop"
msgstr "Firefox ar gyfer y bwrdd gwaith"

#: firefox/new.lang:9
msgid "Different by design"
msgstr "Yn fwriadol wahanol"

#: firefox/new.lang:13
msgid "Proudly<br />non-profit"
msgstr "Yn falch o fod yn<br />ddim er elw"

#: firefox/new.lang:17
msgid "Innovating<br />for you"
msgstr "Arloesi<br />er eich mwyn"

#: firefox/new.lang:21
msgid "Fast, flexible,<br />secure"
msgstr "Cyflym, hyblyg,<br />diogel"

#: firefox/new.lang:25
msgid ""
"As a non-profit, we’re free to innovate on your behalf without any pressure "
"to compromise. You’re going to love the difference."
msgstr ""
"Fel corff ddim er elw, rydym yn rhydd i arloesi ar eich rhan heb orfod "
"cyfaddawdu. Byddwch wrth eich bodd gyda'r gwahaniaeth."

#: firefox/new.lang:29
msgid "Firefox screenshot"
msgstr "Llun sgrin Firefox"

#: firefox/new.lang:33
msgid "Thanks for downloading Firefox!"
msgstr "Diolch am ddewis Firefox!"

#: firefox/new.lang:37
msgid "Start the process by clicking Run."
msgstr "Cychwynnwch y broses drwy glicio Rhedeg."

#: firefox/new.lang:41
msgid ""
"Your download should begin automatically. If not, <a id=\"%s\" href="
"\"\">click here</a>. It could take a few minutes, but it’s worth the wait."
msgstr ""
"Dylai eich llwytho i lawr gychwyn yn syth. Os nad, <a id=\"%s\" href="
"\"\">cliciwch yma</a>. Dylai gymryd ychydig funudau, ond mae'n werth disgwyl."

#: firefox/new.lang:45
msgid ""
"When prompted, drag the Firefox icon into the image of your Applications "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"Pan gewch chi eich annog, llusgwch eicon Firefox i ddelwedd eich ffolder "
"Rhaglenni."

#: firefox/new.lang:49
msgid ""
"Click Run to launch the Mozilla Firefox setup wizard. Then, just follow the "
"steps (we've made the process as painless as possible)."
msgstr ""
"Cliciwch Rhedeg i gychwyn dewin gosod Mozilla Firefox. Yna dilynwch y camau "
"(mae'r broses yn un hawdd iawn)."

#: firefox/new.lang:53
msgid ""
"Drag the Firefox icon from the Applications folder into the dock. Then, just "
"click on Firefox whenever you want to use the web!"
msgstr ""
"Llusgwch eicon Firefox o'r ffolder Rhaglenni i'r doc. Yna cliciwch ar "
"Firefox pryd bynnag rydych eisiau defnyddio'r we!"

#: firefox/new.lang:57
msgid ""
"Now you’re ready to leap boldly into a new era of Web surfing. Double-click "
"on the Firefox icon whenever you want to go online."
msgstr ""
"Nawr rydych yn barod i fentro'n hyderus i gyfnod newydd o syrffio'r we. "
"Rhowch glic dwbl i eicon Firefox pryd bynnag fyddwch eisiau mynd ar-lein."

#: firefox/new.lang:61
msgid "1"
msgstr "1"

#: firefox/new.lang:65
msgid "2"
msgstr "2"

#: firefox/new.lang:69
msgid "3"
msgstr "3"

#. file <title> tag
#: firefox/new.lang:74
msgid "Mozilla Firefox Web Browser"
msgstr "Porwr Gwe Mozilla Firefox"

#. New unified download page: https://www-demo2.allizom.org/en-US/firefox/new/
#: firefox/new.lang:79
msgid "Sorry, Firefox is currently unsupported by iOS devices."
msgstr "Nid yw Firefox yn cael ei gynnal ar ddyfeisiau iOS ar hyn o bryd."

#: firefox/new.lang:83
msgid "Congrats! You’re using the latest version of Firefox."
msgstr "Llongyfarchiadau! Rydych y defnyddio'r fersiwn diweddaraf o Firefox."

#: firefox/new.lang:87
msgid ""
"Looks like you’re using an older version of Firefox. Update on Google Play."
msgstr ""
"Mae'n edrych fel eich bod yn defnyddio hen fersiwn o Firefox. Diweddarwch yn "
"Google Play."

#: firefox/new.lang:91
msgid "Looks like you’re using an older version of Firefox."
msgstr "Mae'n edrych fel eich bod yn defnyddio hen fersiwn o Firefox."

#: firefox/new.lang:95
msgid "Update to stay fast and safe."
msgstr "Diweddarwch i gadw'n gyflym a diogel."

#: firefox/new.lang:99
msgid "Get it free on Google Play"
msgstr "Am ddim o Google Play"

#: firefox/new.lang:103
msgid "Learn more about Firefox for desktop"
msgstr "Dysgu rhagor am Firefox ar y bwrdd gwaith"

#: firefox/new.lang:107
msgid "Need help?"
msgstr "Angen cymorth?"

#: firefox/new.lang:111
msgid "Looking for mobile?"
msgstr "Chwilio am y symudol?"

#: firefox/new.lang:115
msgid "Download a fresh copy"
msgstr "Llwythwch un newydd i lawr"

#: firefox/new.lang:119
msgid "Learn more about Firefox for Mobile"
msgstr "Dysgu rhagor am Firefox Symudol"

#: firefox/new.lang:123
msgid "Learn more about Firefox OS"
msgstr "Dysgu rhagor am Firefox OS"

#: firefox/new.lang:127
msgid "Get Firefox on your Android device"
msgstr "Estyn Firefox ar gyfer Android"

#: firefox/new.lang:131
msgid "Learn about Firefox OS"
msgstr "Dysgu am Firefox OS"

#: firefox/new.lang:135
msgid "Discover all the ways to take Firefox on the go"
msgstr "Darganfod yr holl ffyrdd i ddefnyddio Firefox wrth deithio"

#: firefox/new.lang:139
msgid "Why don’t we offer an iOS version?"
msgstr "Pam nad ydym yn cynnig fersiwn iOS?"

#. The following two strings are used in the <title> tag of the page
#: firefox/new.lang:144
msgid "Download Firefox"
msgstr "Llwytho Firefox i Lawr"

#. Note: 'free' as in free of charge
#: firefox/new.lang:149
msgid "Free Web Browser"
msgstr "Porwr Gwe am Ddim"

#. Meta tag description (visible in the code)
#: firefox/new.lang:154
msgid ""
"Download Mozilla Firefox, a free Web browser. Firefox is created by a global "
"non-profit dedicated to putting individuals in control online. Get Firefox "
"today!"
msgstr ""
"Llwythwch Mozilla Firefox i lawr, mae'n borwr gwe rhydd a rhad. Mae Firefox "
"wedi ei greu gan gorff byd-eang, dim er elw sydd a'i fryd ar roi grym i "
"unigolion ar-lein. Defnyddiwch Firefox heddiw!"

#. Schema.org tag description (visible in the code)
#: firefox/new.lang:159
msgid ""
"Mozilla Firefox, free web browser, is created by a global non-profit "
"dedicated to putting individuals in control &amp; shaping the future of the "
"web for the public good."
msgstr ""
"Crëwyd Mozilla Firefox, porwr gwe rhydd, gan gorff byd eang dim er elw sydd "
"a'i fryd ar osod unigolion wrth y llyw ac yn ffurfio dyfodol y we er lles "
"pawb."
